<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 10:07:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>伊朗袭击后，战争结束的希望在加沙蔓延。很快就消散了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/hope-for-the-wars-end-spread-in-gaza-after-irans-attack-it-dissipated-quickly/0000018e-f033-d240-a19f-f43395680000</link><description>伊朗努塞拉特难民营的一名居民表示，加沙人希望国际社会对以色列施加压力，阻止地区大火，从而加大结束其在加沙行动的压力，但这似乎只会转移人们对加沙的注意力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 09:19:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/hope-for-the-wars-end-spread-in-gaza-after-irans-attack-it-dissipated-quickly/0000018e-f033-d240-a19f-f43395680000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁表示没有义务向以色列国防军招募犹太学生或停止资助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-says-no-obligation-to-draft-yeshiva-students-to-idf-or-halt-their-funding/0000018e-f000-dbb3-a3bf-f5cd55cc0000</link><description>内阁的立场不利于司法部长，预计将在高等法院就此问题提出请愿书时要求一名独立律师。司法部长上周拒绝了这一请求，声称政府尚未就此事表明立场</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 07:52:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-says-no-obligation-to-draft-yeshiva-students-to-idf-or-halt-their-funding/0000018e-f000-dbb3-a3bf-f5cd55cc0000</guid></item><item><title>卫星图像显示伊朗弹道导弹袭击以色列空军基地造成的破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/satellite-image-shows-damage-from-iranian-ballistic-missile-strike-on-israeli-air-base/0000018e-ecba-daad-a3de-eebbd9190000</link><description>照片显示内瓦蒂姆空军基地 C-130 运输机附近滑行道受损，伊朗连夜袭击以色列，该基地遭到四枚弹道导弹袭击</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 03:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/satellite-image-shows-damage-from-iranian-ballistic-missile-strike-on-israeli-air-base/0000018e-ecba-daad-a3de-eebbd9190000</guid></item><item><title>人身威胁和骚扰：伊朗升级针对以色列人的心理战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/personal-threats-and-harassment-iran-escalates-psychological-warfare-against-israel/0000018e-ecc8-dbb3-a3bf-fdcdb1840000</link><description>在政府数据库泄露重要信息、向以色列人质家属发送模拟葬礼花圈以及记者受到威胁后，数十名前公务员收到了来自海外的骚扰电话。 “这是伊朗持续不断的骚扰、制造混乱和分裂社会的行为。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 03:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/personal-threats-and-harassment-iran-escalates-psychological-warfare-against-israel/0000018e-ecc8-dbb3-a3bf-fdcdb1840000</guid></item><item><title>报告：以色列错误估计了伊朗对高级将军被杀的反应，之前“时刻”告诉美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-live/five-idf-reservists-in-serious-condition-following-rocket-drone-strike-on-northern-israel/0000018e-eecd-daad-a3de-eeff299e0000</link><description>报告：以色列在逾越节之前不太可能对伊朗发动袭击 ■ 欧洲领导人在袭击以色列后支持对伊朗实施新制裁 ■ 火箭弹和无人机袭击以色列北部后，五名以色列国防军预备役人员伤势严重 ■ 卡塔尔总理称多哈“重新评估”作用担任以色列-加沙调解人</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 01:28:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-live/five-idf-reservists-in-serious-condition-following-rocket-drone-strike-on-northern-israel/0000018e-eecd-daad-a3de-eeff299e0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管缺乏安全经验，以色列内阁还是批准了本-格维尔任命的部主任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-rubber-stamps-ben-gvirs-pick-as-ministry-chief-despite-lack-of-security-experience/0000018e-ee06-dbb3-a3bf-ffcf41d40000</link><description>审查小组表示，国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔的亲密伙伴拉斐尔·恩格尔“表现出了极大的学习动力”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 22:06:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-rubber-stamps-ben-gvirs-pick-as-ministry-chief-despite-lack-of-security-experience/0000018e-ee06-dbb3-a3bf-ffcf41d40000</guid></item><item><title>近东救济工程处：以色列军队使用酷刑迫使工作人员承认与哈马斯的关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/unrwa-israeli-army-forced-staff-to-confess-ties-to-hamas-using-torture/0000018e-ed4f-d5d5-a59f-ef5f32280000</link><description>联合国巴勒斯坦难民机构发布的一份报告包括被以色列拘留的该机构工作人员的说法，称他们受到威胁和胁迫，承认该机构工作人员参与了 10 月 7 日的哈马斯袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 20:26:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/unrwa-israeli-army-forced-staff-to-confess-ties-to-hamas-using-torture/0000018e-ed4f-d5d5-a59f-ef5f32280000</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚大学校长成为美国反犹太主义战争的最新替罪羊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-17/ty-article/.highlight/columbia-universitys-president-is-the-latest-scapegoat-in-americas-antisemitism-wars/0000018e-ed1c-daad-a3de-ef3fff470000</link><description>这次听证会是自 10 月 7 日以来举行的第四次有关反犹太主义的听证会。但美国人仍然存在严重分歧，很难想象这些听证会如何能够促成合作努力，以平息大学校园中的煽动性言论</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 20:08:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-17/ty-article/.highlight/columbia-universitys-president-is-the-latest-scapegoat-in-americas-antisemitism-wars/0000018e-ed1c-daad-a3de-ef3fff470000</guid></item><item><title>加拿大航空 (Air Canada) 暂停飞往以色列的航班至 5 月底，加入易捷航空 (EasyJet) 行列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/air-canada-suspends-service-to-israel-to-end-of-may-joining-easyjet/0000018e-ed3e-daad-a3de-ef3f38d70000</link><description>加拿大国家航空公司在因加沙战争而中断六个月后，于两周前恢复了飞往以色列的航班。航空业官员担心，与伊朗的紧张局势升级可能会导致更多航空公司效仿其做法</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 18:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/air-canada-suspends-service-to-israel-to-end-of-may-joining-easyjet/0000018e-ed3e-daad-a3de-ef3f38d70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陷入战争，第 194 天：真主党在无人机和导弹袭击以色列北部的情况下造成至少 18 人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-194-hezbollah-wounds-at-least-18-in-missile-attack-on-north-israel/0000018e-ed03-dbb3-a3bf-fdcf89fe0000</link><description>以色列北部真主党火箭弹袭击造成至少 18 人受伤 ■ 美国官员预计以色列将在伊朗领土上进行“有限打击”以回应伊朗袭击 ■ 英国外长：明确表示以色列打算对伊朗袭击作出回应 ■ 伊朗：军方已做好应对任何袭击的准备以色列对袭击“做出严厉回应” ■ 卡塔尔总理：停火谈判正处于“微妙阶段” ■ 战争已过去 194 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:20:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-194-hezbollah-wounds-at-least-18-in-missile-attack-on-north-israel/0000018e-ed03-dbb3-a3bf-fdcf89fe0000</guid></item><item><title>对于 10 月 7 日逃离哈马斯的以色列人来说，高速公路变成了死亡陷阱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-israelis-fleeing-hamas-on-october-7-highways-turned-into-death-traps/0000018e-e196-d052-a78f-e5d690780000</link><description>因巴尔开车去打架，尽管他的女朋友恳求他不要这么做。莎妮设法与她的祖父进行了最后一次视频通话。他们只是加沙边境附近道路上无法躲避哈马斯的 250 多人中的两人</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:34:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-israelis-fleeing-hamas-on-october-7-highways-turned-into-death-traps/0000018e-e196-d052-a78f-e5d690780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军预备役人员情况危急，四人在无人机和导弹对北部的袭击中受重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-reservist-in-critical-condition-4-seriously-wounded-in-drone-rocket-attack-on-north/0000018e-ec8c-daad-a3de-eebfd45c0000</link><description>一架无人机和反坦克导弹袭击以色列北部阿拉伯阿拉姆谢的建筑物，造成 18 人受伤 ■ 以色列军队正在调查为何没有警报器警告无人机袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:26:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-reservist-in-critical-condition-4-seriously-wounded-in-drone-rocket-attack-on-north/0000018e-ec8c-daad-a3de-eebfd45c0000</guid></item><item><title>雷切尔·戈德堡-波林 (Rachel Goldberg-Polin) 入选《时代》杂志 100 名最具影响力人物名单，其儿子赫什在加沙被扣为人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/mother-of-israeli-held-in-gaza-named-to-time-magazines-100-most-influential-people-list/0000018e-ecaa-dbb3-a3bf-fdef93e40000</link><description>戈德堡-波林 23 岁的儿子赫什 (Hersh) 拥有美国和以色列双重国籍，于 10 月 7 日在诺瓦音乐节上被绑架。《时代》杂志的简介将她描述为“人质及其家人最引人注目的倡导者之一”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:19:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/mother-of-israeli-held-in-gaza-named-to-time-magazines-100-most-influential-people-list/0000018e-ecaa-dbb3-a3bf-fdef93e40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列预计年底前将有8000名安全人员遭受心理伤害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/health/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-expects-8-000-security-personnel-with-psychological-injuries-by-years-end/0000018e-ec39-d8eb-af8e-fdff5f000000</link><description>自10月7日以来，以色列国防部康复部门已收治7209名受伤士兵，其中约三分之一患有心理损伤，包括焦虑、抑郁、创伤后应激障碍、适应问题、沟通困难和精神病状态</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:07:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/health/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-expects-8-000-security-personnel-with-psychological-injuries-by-years-end/0000018e-ec39-d8eb-af8e-fdff5f000000</guid></item><item><title>学生处于以色列麦卡锡主义的最前沿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/students-are-at-the-forefront-of-israeli-mccarthyism/0000018e-e5fa-de97-a5bf-f5fad4e80000</link><description>在以色列，学生们并没有像其他国家的学生那样扮演抵抗、反叛和挑战惯例的角色，而是领导着审查制度</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 12:57:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/students-are-at-the-forefront-of-israeli-mccarthyism/0000018e-e5fa-de97-a5bf-f5fad4e80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的战时内阁失去控制，可能导致以色列陷入地区战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-war-cabinet-has-lost-control-and-could-lead-israel-into-a-regional-war/0000018e-ebbb-d8eb-af8e-fbffd6fe0000</link><description>内阁部长们认为，他们未能看到伊朗的导弹和无人机袭击的答案就是进行报复——随着内塔尼亚胡联盟的压力越来越大，他的喋喋不休可能是唯一可以避免鲁莽反应的办法</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 12:25:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-war-cabinet-has-lost-control-and-could-lead-israel-into-a-regional-war/0000018e-ebbb-d8eb-af8e-fbffd6fe0000</guid></item><item><title>两名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸与以色列定居者的冲突中被枪杀。无人被拘留</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-were-fatally-shot-in-a-clash-with-west-bank-settlers-no-one-was-detained/0000018e-e8d0-dba7-a3ee-fcd9a9110000</link><description>纳布卢斯以南巴勒斯坦人和以色列定居者之间冲突的目击者称，士兵当时在场，但直到枪击结束后才采取行动。将尸体带到以色列进行尸检可能有助于将子弹与现场人员进行匹配</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 11:41:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-were-fatally-shot-in-a-clash-with-west-bank-settlers-no-one-was-detained/0000018e-e8d0-dba7-a3ee-fcd9a9110000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗严厉打击头巾法；警方拍摄到当街袭击妇女的画面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/iran-cracks-down-on-hijab-law-police-filmed-attacking-women-in-the-street/0000018e-eb79-d35c-a39e-fb7b15160000</link><description>据伊朗当地媒体报道，新的执法阶段尚未正式宣布，尽管最近在社交媒体上流传的视频显示，妇女遭到身穿制服的警卫的暴力袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 10:41:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/iran-cracks-down-on-hijab-law-police-filmed-attacking-women-in-the-street/0000018e-eb79-d35c-a39e-fb7b15160000</guid></item><item><title>与以色列和美国结盟打击伊朗的阿拉伯国家现在面临后果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/arab-states-that-allied-with-israel-and-u-s-for-iran-attack-now-face-consequences/0000018e-eb42-d35c-a39e-fb6318100000</link><description>阿拉伯国家深知，只有以色列是伊朗的瞄准目标，而且其利益没有受到直接威胁，鉴于加沙攻势，阿拉伯国家现在面临着向公众解释其前所未有的联盟的困难</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:37:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/arab-states-that-allied-with-israel-and-u-s-for-iran-attack-now-face-consequences/0000018e-eb42-d35c-a39e-fb6318100000</guid></item><item><title>英国和德国高级外交官抵达以色列，以缓和其对伊朗的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/british-german-top-diplomats-arrive-in-israel-in-bid-to-temper-its-reaction-to-iran/0000018e-eaef-d35c-a39e-fbef70610000</link><description>卡梅伦和贝尔博克将与几位以色列高级政府官员会面，并警告他们不要进一步升级与德黑兰的紧张局势，此前他们的国家协助以色列挫败了大规模袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:41:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/british-german-top-diplomats-arrive-in-israel-in-bid-to-temper-its-reaction-to-iran/0000018e-eaef-d35c-a39e-fbef70610000</guid></item></channel></rss>